This is a simple template providing standardized formatting for entries in the {{Tlx|Admins}} template. 

'''Usage''':
:{{tlx|Wiki admin|account name|decoration (optional)}}

<code>decoration</code> is optional, and will be placed after the username but before the talk and contribution links. Intended for use with language flags or titles.

'''Note''': The template must be enclosed within a table and does not include a row break character.

'''Example''':
:{{tlx|Wiki admin|Game widow|(Wiki Team Lead) &#91;[File:Flag qc.svg|16px{{!}}Français{{!}}link{{=}}&#93;]}}

'''Result''':
{|
{{Wiki admin|Game widow|(Wiki Team Lead) [[File:Flag qc.svg|16px|Français|link=]]}}
|}
